<h3>
    Freelance Web &amp; Graphic Designer, Freelance Photographer<br>
    <span class="normal">Hypertexthero, Worldwide<br>
    2005–Present</span>
</h3>

<p>
    Completed a variety of web, print and photography projects for clients around the world, from large companies in London and internet start-ups in Silicon Valley to non-profits and United Nations agencies in Rome.
</p>

